     (a) you retain this license and all copyright notices in copies and
         derivatives; and
     (b) you operate any Instance you deploy in compliance with Section 5
         (Responsibility).

4. GRANT — COMMERCIAL INSTANCES

   If your team or organization would like a formal license agreement — for
   procurement, legal compliance, or to support the project — we offer
